				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span class="storyText"><a href="http://www.reuters.com/locales/newsArticle.jsp?type=technologyNews&amp;locale=en_IN&amp;storyID=4032368">Reuters</a>: &#8220;Verizon said Monday that its initial [fiber] deployment plans involve about 1<br />
